Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: k. b. b. b.
des:
Around the clock hosted music bringing you the best and most popular tunes of the last thirty years - music from the nineties, 2K, and today!

Coming to you live from the KBBB 102.5 FM studios in Bay City, Texas, with American announcers.

To start, just say "Alexa, play KBBB", or "Alexa, open KBBB". You can ask Alexa the name of any song by saying "Alexa, ask KBBB what's this song?". And, to stop the stream, simply say "Alexa, stop".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
